<ul style=3D"list-style-type: disc; padding-left: 40px; margin: 16px 0;">=
=09<li style=3D"margin-bottom: 5px;">Prosecutors will argue that the combin=
ation of (1) FTX spending millions of dollars on luxury apartments for Bank=
man-Fried and (2) $8 billion of FTX customer money going missing is=C2=A0<e=
m>pretty suspicious!=C2=A0</em>Like, that=E2=80=99s the main thing that=C2=
