ury goods and experiences for yourself, and at the end you have the luxury =
goods and the customers don=E2=80=99t have the money.</li>=09<li style=3D"m=
argin-bottom: 5px;">Bankman-Fried <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbus=
iness.com/click/32765671.258423/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cubnl0aW1lcy5jb20vbGl2ZS8yMDI=
