<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">In any case yesterday FTX=E2=80=99s bankruptcy=
 estate <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/32765671.2=
58423/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmxvb21iZXJnLmNvbS9uZXdzL2FydGljbGVzLzIwMjMtMDktMTkvZ=
nR4LXN1ZXMtc2FtLWJhbmttYW4tZnJpZWQtcy1wYXJlbnRzLXRvLWNsYXctYmFjay1mdW5kcz9j=
