ors.</p></blockquote>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">And private jets:</p>
<blockquote><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Bankman was richly rewarded for he=
lping perpetuate the FTX Insiders=E2=80=99 fraud. He received millions of d=
ollars in unearned =E2=80=9Cgifts=E2=80=9D and real property, flew on priva=
tely-chartered jets, expensed $1,200 per night hotel stays to the FTX Group=
 =E2=80=A6</p></blockquote>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">And political donations:</p>
<blockquote><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Fried served as the single most in=
fluential advisor regarding Bankman-Fried=E2=80=99s and the FTX Group=E2=80=
=99s political contributions, and repeatedly =E2=80=9Cdunned,=E2=80=9D or c=
alled upon, Bankman-Fried and Singh to contribute millions of dollars direc=
tly to Mind the Gap, Inc. (=E2=80=9CMTG=E2=80=9D), a political action commi=
ttee that she co-founded and for which she served as President and Chairwom=
an, or the organizations MTG supported.</p></blockquote>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">And Super Bowl ads:</p>
<blockquote><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">At his request, Bankman received a=
 cameo appearance alongside Larry David in a now-infamous 2022 FTX Super Bo=
wl commercial. Bankman pushed for his role in the commercial, stating blunt=
ly, =E2=80=9COK, I=E2=80=99m not a starfucker and don=E2=80=99t really care=
