ckquote>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">And now the FTX bankruptcy estate wants the mo=
ney back, basically on the theory that it was customer money and Bankman an=
d Fried shouldn=E2=80=99t get to keep it.<a class=3D"footnote-index" href=
=3D"#footnote-5" style=3D"color: #000000; text-decoration: none !important;=
 border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-styl=
e: none !important; background-color: transparent !important; display: inli=
ne-block;">
<span>[5]</span>
</a></p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">But also on the theory that Bankman and Fried =
knew, or should have known, that it was customer money and not really on th=
