oops. Also her academic work has some=C2=A0ironic titles:</p>
<blockquote><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Fried is a professor emerita of St=
anford Law School and joined its faculty in 1987. Fried has published more =
than three dozen legal and academic writings, including pieces entitled =E2=
=80=9CThe Limits of Personal Responsibility=E2=80=9D and =E2=80=9CBeyond Bl=
ame.=E2=80=9D</p></blockquote>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">There=E2=80=99s a reason the complaint calls o=
ut those titles <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/32=
765671.258423/aHR0cHM6Ly9wYXBlcnMuc3Nybi5jb20vc29sMy9jZl9kZXYvQWJzQnlBdXRoL=
mNmbT9wZXJfaWQ9MjI2MDY/607f07ceef4b8524a319a23cB3a8b37cf" itemprop=3D"Story=
Link" itemscope=3D"itemscope" target=3D"_blank" style=3D"color: #000000; te=
xt-decoration: none !important; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-col=
or: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;"> and not<=
/a> =E2=80=9CLeft Libertarianism: A Review Essay=E2=80=9D or =E2=80=9CCan C=
ontractualism Save Us from Aggregation?=E2=80=9D or =E2=80=9CBegging the Qu=
estion with Style: <em>Anarchy, State and Utopia</em> at Thirty Years.=E2=
