ration: none !important; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #00=
0000; border-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;"> a receipt that =
you then burned</a>, you got nothing at all tangible, but you got cultural =
cachet. You gave Klein money, and he did a prank on you, and then you laugh=
ed about it=C2=A0<em>together</em>, which proved that you were cool in a wa=
y that hanging an Old Master in your dining room could not. You got exactly=
 what you paid for. And Klein got the money.<a class=3D"footnote-index" hre=
